high_descs: Move forward to the blue toaster on the counter between the gray coffee maker and the white refrigerator.
Pick up the potato in front of the blue toaster from the counter.
Turn left and move to the black microwave to the right of the range.
Open the microwave, place the potato on the plate in the microwave, heat the potato using the microwave, open the microwave, pick up the potato, and then close the microwave door.
Turn left, move around the counter to the window, turn right and move to the white door, then turn right and face the black rubbish bin to the left of the yellow chair.
Place the potato in the rubbish bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato in the rubbish bin.

high_descs: Go forward, turn left, go forward, turn right, go forward to the counter with the toaster on it to the left of the fridge.
Take the potato from in front of the toaster.
Turn left, go forward to the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave, take the potato from the microwave.
Turn left, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward past the end of the counter, turn right, go forward to the window, turn right, go forward to the door, turn right to the trash bin.
Put the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in a trash bin.

high_descs: Walk over to the section of counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the potato off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave.
Microwave the potato for a couple seconds to get it hot, then take it out of the microwave.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk around the counter to the small black bin next to the chairs on the other side.
Put the heated potato in the small black bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in a small black bin.
